## Intervention Selection Logic

| Condition | Intervention Type | Action |
|-----------|-------------------|--------|
| days_since_practice >= 7 | escalation | Alert Administrator, plan restart |
| days_since_practice >= 3 | encouragement | Gentle reminder, low-friction re-entry |
| automaticity_decline > 0.2 | support | Identify blockers, adjust difficulty |
| intervention_needed = true | support | Coaching session offer |
| otherwise | none | No intervention needed |

## Output Format

